Hi Maria,

Thank you for calling in this morning.

I've reviewed your policy and can confirm that it does not include any rent=
al benefit. This means that any rental arrangements you choose to make will=
 be at your own expense.

If you have any questions or need further clarification, feel free to reach=
 out to your claim's handler Arnold on 09 960 3249.

Have a pleasant day.


Kind Regards,
[cid:image001.png@01DC159E.F90B5DC0]
Elesi V (She/Her)
Claims Consultant
