break-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Hi Maria,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for calling in this morning.<o:p></o:p></p=
>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I&#8217;ve reviewed your policy and can confirm that=
 it does not include any rental benefit. This means that any rental arrange=
ments you choose to make will be at your own expense.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">If you have any questions or need further clarificat=
ion, feel free to reach out to your claim&#8217;s handler Arnold on
<span lang=3D"en-FJ">09 960 3249</span><span lang=3D"EN-US">.<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Have a pleasant day.<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"en-FJ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
